{"about_the_game":"The award-winning <i><strong>Eagle Island</strong></i> is a roguelite action-platformer that offers a unique blend of falconry-inspired combat mechanics, procedurally generated levels, and challenging boss fights. Players can choose between the narrative-driven story or speed-runner-like rogue mode, mixing and matching 85 abilities to diversify their gameplay.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/Eagle_Island_Montage.gif?t=1709580045\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">OVER 85 ABILITIES &amp; PROCEDURALLY-GENERATED LEVELS IN CLASSIC MODE</h2>&quot;Throw&quot; your owl companion into battle imbued with special abilities! Explore procedurally-generated worlds, set to a beautifully modernized pixel art aesthetic. Levels are also packed with secrets and areas to explore.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/Power_Ups.gif?t=1709580045\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE MORE IN HANDCRAFTED TWIST MODE</h2>In Eagle Island TWIST, you'll experience 45 carefully crafted, retro-themed stages that can be traversed on a 16-bit era world map. TWIST offers even more content to an already well-rounded game, providing a range of mini-games to supplement Classic Mode's roguelite feel.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/Twist_Map.gif?t=1709580045\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LOADED WITH ACCESSIBILITY FEATURES</h2>There are over 18 accessibility settings that can be easily enabled--Such as: remappable controls, difficulty options, text visibility, high contrast, and toggles for flashing and screen shaking.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/681110/extras/Menu_2.gif?t=1709580045\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Apprentice of Elements","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic